    <item>
      <title>习近平避开特朗普早期的关税，为中国争取时间影响美国</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/xi-dodges-early-trump-tariffs-buying-china-time-to-influence-us</link>
      <description><![CDATA[对于国家主席习近平来说，唐纳德·特朗普的总统任期开局本来会很火爆，此前他在竞选时曾承诺要用关税惩罚中国。然而，这位美国领导人上任第一天就为北京赢得了意想不到的喘息空间。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/xi-dodges-early-trump-tariffs-buying-china-time-to-influence-us</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 05:41:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>舒尔茨和梅尔茨在达沃斯论坛上展开德国大选之争</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/davos-2025-scholz-and-merz-take-german-election-battle-to-the-wef-crowd</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国领导人的竞争正转向瑞士，在达沃斯举行的竞选活动中，各方将展示如何重振欧洲最大经济体的不同愿景。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/davos-2025-scholz-and-merz-take-german-election-battle-to-the-wef-crowd</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>里夫斯警告投资者不会相信未来的支出削减</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/reeves-warned-investors-won-t-believe-in-future-spending-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[如果财政大臣雷切尔·里夫斯 (Rachel Reeves) 宣布进一步推迟支出限制，她将很难让金融城相信她的财政信誉，因为她已经试图将有政治争议的决定推迟到工党议会任期的结束阶段。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/reeves-warned-investors-won-t-believe-in-future-spending-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马克龙将于 5 月在亚洲顶级防务峰会上发表主旨演讲</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/macron-to-deliver-keynote-at-asia-s-top-defense-summit-in-may</link>
      <description><![CDATA[国际战略研究所周二宣布，法国总统埃马纽埃尔·马克龙将在今年晚些时候在新加坡举行的亚洲首要防务峰会上发表主旨演讲。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/macron-to-deliver-keynote-at-asia-s-top-defense-summit-in-may</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 04:57:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国前总统尹某在庭审中表示不相信自由民主</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/south-korea-s-arrested-president-to-appear-at-impeachment-trial</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国总统尹锡烈周二首次出席弹劾审判，他表示自己坚信自由民主，该审判针对他上个月令人震惊的短暂戒严令实施。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/south-korea-s-arrested-president-to-appear-at-impeachment-trial</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 01:52:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普计划在 2 月 1 日前对墨西哥、加拿大征收 25% 关税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/trump-plans-to-enact-25-tariffs-on-mexico-canada-by-feb-1</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统唐纳德·特朗普表示，他计划在 2 月 1 日之前对墨西哥和加拿大征收高达 25% 的关税，重申了他的观点，即美国的两个近邻正在让无证移民和毒品涌入该国。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/trump-plans-to-enact-25-tariffs-on-mexico-canada-by-feb-1</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 00:57:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普行政措施概述，从关税到移民</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-20/trump-executive-orders-tariffs-immigration-energy-among-top-priorities</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普总统立即宣布了实施其许多竞选承诺的措施，包括移民、能源、军事和联邦劳动力等方面的政策，其中许多政策被视为推翻其前任乔·拜登的政策。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-20/trump-executive-orders-tariffs-immigration-energy-among-top-priorities</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 20 Jan 2025 21:12:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
